RawDataSet2 <- list.files(pattern = "yP32_") %>%
  lapply(read_csv) %>% 
  bind_rows%>%
  mutate(Subject= rep(list.files(pattern = "yP32_"), each=329))%>%
  separate(`IT1 IT2 KEY RT`,c("IT1","a", "IT2","b","c","d","e","f","g","KEY", "RT"), sep = " ")%>%
  select(Subject,IT1,IT2,KEY,RT)%>%
  filter(IT1 != "S",
         IT1 !="DESCANSO")%>%
  mutate(Rubric = if_else(IT1 ==IT2, "m", "n"),
         Accuracy = if_else(KEY == Rubric, 1, 0),
         RT = as.numeric(RT))%>%
  group_by(Subject)%>%
  slice(4:327)%>%
  ungroup()
